[[File:WasakaPudding.jpg|thumb|right|120px|[[Lumpawaroo/Legends|Lumpy]] enjoys his mother's wasaka-berry pudding.]]

'''Wasaka-berry pudding''' was a delicacy on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] made from [[Wasaka berry/Legends|wasaka berries]] that grew in the [[Shadowlands/Legends|Shadowlands]]. Wasaka-berry pudding was a favorite dish of [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca's]]. Despite [[Lumpawaroo/Legends|Lumpy's]] valiant efforts to obtain the berries, Chewbacca's wife, [[Mallatobuck/Legends|Mallatobuck]], was unable to make the pudding for his 200th [[Birthday/Legends|birthday]].

